    h2.text-4xl.font-black.mb-4 What about Scoutbook?

    p.leading-snug.text-2xl.font-light.mb-8 While there's a bit of overlap, Scoutbook covers different ground by focusing on advancement. Scoutplan is entirely focused on <strong class="font-bold">event management and communication</strong>. Together, the two make a potent combination.

